Text:
Notes.txt has the link to where the patch came from and the installer was downloaded from Sandboxie.com

Also I only tested the 64bit version.
I used the patch in a sandbox LOL

I made a mistake when I stated that Sandboxie will still say Unregistered after applying the patch. I simply forgot to reboot my computer lol

The 30 day trial nag window popped up on me and thought WTF ? is the patcher bad ??
Naw I'm just an idiot ;)
